n A species can share habitat with others
n WHERE an organism lives
n Example: Tiger lives in tropical forest
NICHE
"Profession" of an organism
n Functional role in the ecosystem
n Food, behaviour, timing, interactions
n Includes ALL ecological requirements
n No two species share exact same niche
n WHAT an organism does (+ where, when)
n Example: Tiger is apex predator, eats deer
